resting. I think I got that idea from reading some tech notes from Ian Bell coming with his Tank demo, where it says he's cycle counting in order to know the position of the beam or somesuch? Maybe I just misunderstood that part.<br /><br /><div class="quotetitle">tokumaru wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">As Bregalad suggested, you can turn rendering off manually for a few extra scanlines of PPU access.</div>
